<size=21>CSM SEPARATION checklist</size>

Panel 1
	Set DET 59:30
Panel 8
	cb SECS LOGIC (2) - closed (verify)
	cb SECS ARM BAT (2) - closed (verify)
	SECS LOGIC (2) - on (up)(verify)
Panel 2
	RCS CMD - ON (2s then OFF)
Panel 8
	SECS PYRO ARM (2) - ARM

When ready for CM Sep: Panel 1
	Start DET up
	EMS MODE - NORM
	CMC MODE - AUTO
At DET 00:00
	CSM LV SEP - push
Panel 2
	SM RCS PRIM PRPLNT tb (4) - gray (verify)
	SM RCS He tb (8) - gray (verify)
	SM RCS SEC FUEL PRESS (4) - CLOSE
Panel 3
	FC REACS VALVES - NORM

<size=21>CSM TRANSPOSITION checklist</size>

Panel 1
	Thrust ±X to ~-101.0 fps on EMS counter
	BMAG MODE ROLL - ATT 1/RATE 2
	BMAG MODE PITCH - ATT 1/RATE 2
	BMAG MODE YAW - ATT 1/RATE 2
	SC CONT - SCS
	(Coast for 1 MIN 10 SEC Distance 70 ft)
	Thrust ±X to ~-100.5 fps on EMS counter
	MAN ATT PITCH - ACCEL CMD (verify)
	(Pitch up 180° at 5°/sec)
	MAN ATT PITCH - RATE CMD (after 180° pitch)
	BMAG MODE ROLL - RATE 2
	BMAG MODE PITCH - RATE 2
	BMAG MODE YAW - RATE 2
	(Roll left 60° at 2°/sec)
	SC CONT - CMC
	Thrust ±X to ~-101.0 fps on EMS counter
	(Station-keep with S-IVB)

	SECS PYRO ARM (2) - SAFE
	SECS LOGIC (2) - off
	SECS ARM BAT cb (2) - open
Panel 278

	RHC PWR DIR (2) - OFF
Panel 8
	cb RCS LOGIC (2) - open
	cb EDS (3) - open
